      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARRY TIME (3) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 5th and beaten only 2.75 lengths (22.91) at Warrnambool. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. PARTY STARTER (8) made an impressive debut when was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a scorching early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 13 length third (26.82) over 460m at this track. Shows good promise and should be in this for a long way. PAW WARRINGAH (1) profiles well and boxed nicely for his debut. Among the leading players. PARTY STEPS (2) is a newcomer from the Krystiana Dubos kennel. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
